prompt:
Simplify keys.nix: drop premature main/all grouping, use a single flat host list.

## Context
PR #411, branch fix/microvms-and-secrets. The current keys.nix has named host keys (good) but splits them into main/all groups that aren't meaningfully used — every secret in secrets.nix uses keys.hosts.main, making the grouping pointless. Simplify to a single list.

## Changes to make

### secrets/keys.nix
Replace the current structure with:

