### Do NOT touch .age files
Do NOT re-encrypt or modify any .age files. The user will run `agenix --rekey` manually after this change.

### Do NOT touch any other files
Only modify secrets/keys.nix and secrets/secrets.nix. Do not touch flake.nix, host configs, or module configs.

## Acceptance criteria
- keys.nix has named host variables but a single flat hosts list
- secrets.nix uses keys.users ++ keys.hosts everywhere
- No .age files modified
- No other files modified
